---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '@components/ui/Button.astro';
import Lightbox from '@components/ui/Lightbox.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Olympia Fitness - Case Study"
  description="A comprehensive fitness tracking application with AI-powered workout recommendations."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-700 to-blue-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">Mobile App</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">iOS</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">Android</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm">Capacitor</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
          Olympia Fitness
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80">
          A performance tracking application for CSCS trainers to administer tests, track athlete progress, and share results with parents.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Screenshots Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-8 text-center">App Screenshots</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/olympia-fitness/screenshot-1.png" alt="Olympia Fitness screenshot 1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity lightbox-img" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/olympia-fitness/screenshot-2.png" alt="Olympia Fitness screenshot 2" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity lightbox-img" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/olympia-fitness/screenshot-3.png" alt="Olympia Fitness screenshot 3" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity lightbox-img" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/olympia-fitness/screenshot-4.png" alt="Olympia Fitness screenshot 4" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity lightbox-img" />
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/olympia-fitness/id6473857575" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors font-semibold">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
          View on App Store
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">Overview</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The Olympia Fitness app is used to track and monitor the progress of athlete's training in Cranston, RI. The app assists Olympia's CSCS trainers administer performance testing, allows them to choose what tests to administer, quickly look up how the test is administered, attach photos and videos to tests, and review/share results with parents.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Challenge Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">The Challenge</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
        <p>
          Delivering a comprehensive suite of tools to an operating business with minimal disruption. Trainers used to track results with pen and paper, and scanned the results to the computer, making it hard to show progress over time. Additionally, there weren't any good ways to show how their child compared to other children of similar age with similar goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">Our Solution</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
        <p>
          The Olympia Fitness app is tailor-made to the workflow of Olympia Fitness and Performance RI. The app allows trainers to pull up the results of any athlete in the system and review their results at a glance. Parents can be added to athlete accounts allowing them to track their child's performance over time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Additionally, the app has a leaderboard broken down by Age and Sex which helps athletes see how they compare against their peers. Finally, the trainers can use the results and the attached videos to help them create targeted programming to ensure the athletes are maximally likely to meet their goals.
        </p>
        <p>
          The app was created using the Cursor IDE and leveraged a variety of AI models including Claude Sonnet, Grok Code Fast, Gemini Pro, and Claude Opus.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
        <div class="p-6 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Technology Stack</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Angular</li>
            <li>Ionic / Capacitor</li>
            <li>Supabase</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Key Features</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Performance Test Administration</li>
            <li>Photo & Video Attachments</li>
            <li>Parent Access & Sharing</li>
            <li>Age/Sex Leaderboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
        Want Similar Results?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Let's discuss how we can help build your fitness or health application.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button href="/contact" variant="accent" size="lg">
          Start Your Project
        </Button>
        <Button href="/portfolio" variant="secondary" size="lg">
          View More Projects
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Lightbox />
</BaseLayout>
